📄 AI Document Understanding & Fraud Detection Agent

🚀 Overview

This project uses Azure AI Content Understanding and an AI Agent (GPT-4.1) to extract information from documents and detect fraud automatically.

It can process invoices, contracts, and financial documents by converting them into structured JSON and analyzing them for suspicious activity.

⚙️ How It Works

Upload a document or image
AI extracts data and converts it into JSON
AI agent analyzes the data
System returns result: REAL, FAKE, SUSPICIOUS, or INVALID

🧠 Features

Extract text, tables, and key data from documents
Convert documents into structured JSON
Detect fraud or inconsistencies
Simple AI classification with explanation


🎯 Use Cases

Invoice verification
Fraud detection
Document validation
Financial checks
